data.description: Former model home with over 3600sf and 2 MASTER BEDROOMS!!  The home has just been renovated with NEW interior paint and NEW carpet.  HUGE kitchen with an endless row of cherry cabinets and granite counters.  Impressive floorplan with high vaulted ceilings, 5 bedrooms PLUS a loft.  And you have to check out the theater room with tiered seating and movie-themed carpet.  The largest master bedroom is downstairs, and the ensuite bath includes double sinks and a separate tub & shower. There are ceiling fans and 2'' blinds in every room.  Exit to the backyard to find a covered patio that spans the entire width of the house, and a fireplace for your evening gatherings.  The home backs to a common area for added privacy.  $116/sf is a steal of a price--see this beautiful property in person today!
